---
export const prerender = true;
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---
<BlogLayout title="Scrabble Words Starting With Z — ZEPHYR, ZENITH, ZEALOT & ZOMBIE" description="High-scoring Scrabble words starting with Z. ZEPHYR (23pts), ZOMBIE (19pts), ZENITH (18pts), ZEALOT (15pts). Z-word strategy and premium square placement." keywords="scrabble words starting with z, zephyr scrabble, zenith scrabble word, zealot scrabble, zombie scrabble, z words scrabble, words beginning with z">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Article","headline":"Scrabble Words Starting With Z — ZEPHYR, ZENITH, ZEALOT & ZOMBIE","description":"High-scoring Scrabble words starting with Z. ZEPHYR (23pts), ZOMBIE (19pts), ZENITH (18pts), ZEALOT (15pts).","datePublished":"2026-06-29","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"ScrabbleWordsFinder.com","url":"https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com"},"publisher":{"@type":"Organization","name":"ScrabbleWordsFinder.com"},"mainEntityOfPage":{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com/blog/scrabble-words-starting-with-z"}})} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What Scrabble words starting with Z score highest?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"ZEPHYR scores 23 points (Z=10, E=1, P=3, H=4, Y=4, R=1), ZOMBIE scores 19 points, ZENITH scores 18 points (Z=10, E=1, N=1, I=1, T=1, H=4), and ZEALOT scores 15 points."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is ZOMBIE a valid Scrabble word?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, ZOMBIE is valid in both TWL and SOWPODS, scoring 19 points. It pluralises to ZOMBIES (21pts) for a potential 7-letter bingo play worth 71 points with the bonus."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How many Z-starting words are in the Scrabble dictionary?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"SOWPODS contains over 1,000 words starting with Z, from the 2-letter ZA and ZO to longer words like ZEPHYR, ZENITH, and ZOMBIFIED. Z is worth 10 points — the joint-highest tile value alongside Q."}}]})} />
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose flex items-center gap-1"><a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a><span class="mx-1">›</span><span class="text-gray-300">Letter Guides</span></nav>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Scrabble Words Starting With Z — ZEPHYR, ZENITH, ZEALOT & ZOMBIE</h1>
      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400"><time datetime="2026-06-29">June 29, 2026</time><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><span>5 min read</span><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔤</span> Word Finder</a></div>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Z is worth 10 points — tied with Q for the highest tile value in Scrabble. Words starting with Z guarantee those 10 points hit the board, and many pair Z with other high-value letters like Y (4pts), H (4pts), and P (3pts) to create scoring powerhouses.</p>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">23 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">ZEPHYR</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">19 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">ZOMBIE</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">18 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">ZENITH</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">15 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">ZEALOT</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Top Z-Starting Words</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10"><p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🌬️ ZEPHYR — 23 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Z(10)+E(1)+P(3)+H(4)+Y(4)+R(1). Stacks Z with P, H, and Y. Devastating.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10"><p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🧟 ZOMBIE — 19 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Z(10)+O(1)+M(3)+B(3)+I(1)+E(1). Extends to ZOMBIES for bingo potential.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10"><p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">⭐ ZENITH — 18 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Z(10)+E(1)+N(1)+I(1)+T(1)+H(4). Z plus H gives 14 from two tiles alone.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10"><p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🔥 ZEALOT — 15 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Z(10)+E(1)+A(1)+L(1)+O(1)+T(1). All common tiles after Z. Easy to form.</p></div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Why Z-Starters Dominate</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 Scoring Floor</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">Z-starting words score an average of <span class="text-white font-medium">16+ points</span> because Z itself provides 10 points as a floor. Compare with E-starting words averaging 7-8 points. Leading with Z is always a strong play when the board allows it.</p>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">More Z-Starters Worth Knowing</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">ZAPPY</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">21 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">ZIPPY</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">21 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">ZILCH</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">19 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">ZONK</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">17 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">ZAP</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">14 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">ZA</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">11 pts</span></span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Strategy for Z-Starting Plays</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">ZEPHYR on a DWS:</span> At 23 base points, a Double Word Score gives you 46 points from one word. The Y and H also benefit from doubling, making this one of the highest non-bingo plays possible.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">ZOMBIE extends to bingo:</span> ZOMBIES is 7 letters (21pts + 50 bonus = 71 total). If you draw Z, O, M, B, I, E, S — that's a natural bingo with common tiles.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">ZA is your 2-letter ace:</span> ZA (11pts) is one of the highest-scoring 2-letter words. Use it for parallel plays — placing ZA next to existing words creates multi-word scores in tight board situations.</p></div>
      </div>
      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Related Articles</h3>
        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <a href="/blog/8-letter-words-with-z/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">8-Letter Words With Z — Bingo Territory</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/best-z-words-scrabble/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Best Z Words in Scrabble — Complete Guide</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/scrabble-words-starting-with-x/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Words Starting With X — XYLOPHONE, XENON & More</span></a>
        </div>
      </aside>
      <div class="not-prose mt-10 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-blue-800/20 border border-blue-800 rounded-xl"><div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap"><p class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-medium">🔤 Try our free Scrabble Word Finder — instant results, no signup</p><a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-400 text-gray-950 text-sm font-semibold transition-colors">Open Word Finder →</a></div></div>
      <div class="not-prose mt-8 text-center"><a href="/blog/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Back to all articles</a></div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
